Hi! Were the team behind Muze.

Some of us started running paid ads and building online businesses as students. Others were shipping software early in their careers, long before most teams would trust them with real ad budgets.


We have always focused on building things that actually work and scale. That mindset is what brought us together.


Over the years, we helped scale e-commerce brands, SaaS companies, and agencies by working hands-on with Meta and Google Ads. We were inside ad accounts every day, testing creatives, managing budgets, building systems, and solving problems most agencies and tools never talk about.


By 2026, performance marketing will be powered by AI, whether teams are ready or not. Manual workflows, slow agencies, and bloated ad teams will not survive the shift.


Now, we are building the tool we always wished existed.


Muze turns everything we learned into an autonomous AI ads team built for the AI-first future of performance marketing.
